<h2 id="beginning" class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Art at the Beginning</h2>
<p>When starting to think about art we knew that we wanted to have a less detailed style that leaned towards brighter natural colors. We decided that the Scavengers Reign fit this style the best.The world we were making is wacky with absurd characters and abilities and thus wanted our art to reflect that. This meant taking some inspiration from adventure time to incorporate strange creatures and comedic elements of modern technology into the world.</p>
<p class="mt-2">Check out our art inspiration here:</p>
